Text: I only tried this on 9.0.0.0 so if you do try it on a higher version please post the information. GPSoft are good at banning certificates so I'm sure they've done it with this if you try to update and/or import settings to a new version.

Definitely not working on versions above 9.0.0.0 so don't waste your time installing newer versions. 

I wonder why there's no crack for this app?
